### =========================

### DATA ISOLATION TEST

### COMPANY SEES ONLY ITS APPLICATIONS

### =========================

GET http://localhost:8080/applications/company
Authorization: {{companyToken}}

### Copy `applicationId` from /applications/company response and paste below
@applicationId = 9

### COMPANY SHORRTLISTS TOP 5 STUDENTS BASED ON FIT SCORE
GET http://localhost:8080/applications/company/shortlist
Authorization: {{companyToken}}


### JOB SPECIFIC SHORTLIST
GET http://localhost:8080/applications/company/shortlist/6?limit=3&minScore=50
Authorization: {{companyToken}}

### SHORTLIST AN APPLICATION
PUT http://localhost:8080/applications/{{applicationId}}/status?status=SHORTLISTED
Authorization: {{companyToken}}

### REJECT AN APPLICATION
PUT http://localhost:8080/applications/{{applicationId}}/status?status=REJECTED
Authorization: {{companyToken}}



